{"tha-ap449:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap449:0.2":"Vibhitakavagga ","tha-ap449:0.3":"Sihasanikattheraapadana ","tha-ap449:1.1":"“Padumuttarassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap449:1.2":"Sabbabhutahitesino; ","tha-ap449:1.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap449:1.4":"Sihasanamadasaham. ","tha-ap449:2.1":"Devaloke manusse va, ","tha-ap449:2.2":"yattha yattha vasamaham; ","tha-ap449:2.3":"Labhami vipulam byamham, ","tha-ap449:2.4":"sihasanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap449:3.1":"Sonnamaya rupimaya, ","tha-ap449:3.2":"lohitangamaya bahu; ","tha-ap449:3.3":"Manimaya ca pallanka, ","tha-ap449:3.4":"nibbattanti mamam sada. ","tha-ap449:4.1":"Bodhiya asanam katva, ","tha-ap449:4.2":"jalajuttamanamino; ","tha-ap449:4.3":"Ucce kule pajayami, ","tha-ap449:4.4":"aho dhammasudhammata. ","tha-ap449:5.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap449:5.2":"sihasanamakasaham; ","tha-ap449:5.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap449:5.4":"sihasanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap449:6.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap449:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap449:6.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap449:7.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap449:7.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap449:7.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap449:8.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap449:8.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap449:8.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap449:9.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sihasaniko thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap449:10.1":"Sihasanikattherassapadanam sattamam. "}